Package dqm.jku.dqmeerkat.quality.profilingstatistics

This package contains the abstract class for profiling statistics and some helper classes for them. The implementations of the profiling statistics are found in the dqm.jku.dqmeerkat.quality.profilingstatistics.singlecolumn and in the dqm.jku.dqmeerkat.quality.profilingstatistics.multicolumn packages.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    DependentProfileStatistic
    Second hierarchy level of abstract base class for profile statistics, its main use is to provide methods for including dependent statistics.
    ProfileStatistic
    Abstract class describing the basic structure for a profilestatistic
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    StatisticCategory
    Enumeration for different DP metric categories
    StatisticTitle
    Enumeration for all DP metrics
